---
name: "faq-answer"
description: "Answer a user question with a concise FAQ-style response"
variables:
  - name: question
    type: string
    required: true
  - name: knowledgeBaseTopic
    type: string
    required: false
---
{% section 'prompt' %}
Answer the following question in 3-5 sentences.
If relevant, reference {{ knowledgeBaseTopic | default: 'the product documentation' }}.
Question: {{ question }}
{% endsection %}
